  "text": "The overall desirability function D is obtained from the individual desirabilities (d i ) using Equation 2. It can provide a way to assess the quality according to one property, the overall Dvalue. By mapping all properties onto a desirability scale between 0 and 1, the individual desirability scores due to multiple properties may be easily combined as a geometric mean even if the properties have different scales or units of measurement [CITATION_1] .",
